style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Resort bases are special star bases built at sce=
nic
locations throughout the galaxy. Scenic locations can include the following=
:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l=
